        <div class="pageDescription"><p align="left">The Press and Information Unit works as the information adviser for the political and administrative management, as well as for the seven departements. </p>
<p align="left">The Unit is responsible for:</p>
<ul type="disc">
<li>Communication strategy, information initiatives, and press service for the Ministry of Justice&nbsp; </li>
<li>Advising the political and administrative management </li>
<li>Editing the Ministry's web site and&nbsp;internal web</li></ul></div>        
